message.body: Hey buddy, you in NorCal for the holidays?
They cancelled my flight so I'm still in Princeton until tomorrow
Ah k I'll be here till Tuesday, then back on the 7th--any chance you'll be around by then?
Cool! I'm thinking of driving down to south bay tomorrow once the weather clears up. I know it's Xmas eve but let me know if you'd have time to meet up briefly!
